node.text:
Tommy has fallen on hard times, so local surfers in California surprised their beloved friend with a new van. One surfer Kenny ( @kennycfong )went out on a limb and bought it and the surfer community stepped up with donations. Karen who sent us this story directly tells Good News Movement, “He's always positive, and complimentary of everyone's waves, and is a talented singer, guitar player and surfer too.” 

Enjoy, Tommy! 🏄 
Video courtesy: @raymondjoycephotography @rjpsurfing

After half of her face was paralyzed in a car accident 20 years ago, Thailand native Malinda Herman didn’t want to show her face to anyone for some time. Her son bought her a guitar to help her through that difficult period. The now 71-year-old loves singing with her dogs and cat. 😃🎶🐶😺🎵.

'Beautiful Sunday' was written by Daniel Boone. A happy & beautiful Sunday to you all!
(Malinda Herman Official)
